{"tid":1496644,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「急」推到將軍澳斬人刀手改判傷人17","createTime":"2019-08-22T15:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T04:51:13.000Z","uid":268109,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"17ed24647bf04efde97660932be5263ea65700f9","tid":1496644,"uid":268109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:23:13.000Z","msg":"各位同伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信大家都有留意將軍澳連儂將斬人事件，<br />\n而凶徒亦於今日22/08第一次提堂，<br />\n而控方所提出的檢控是，<br />\n《香港法例》第212章《侵害人身罪條例》<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 第19條<br />\n「傷人或對他人身體加以嚴重傷害<br />\n任何人非法及惡意傷害他人或對他人身體加以嚴重傷害，不論是否使用武器或器具，均屬犯可循公訴程序審訊的罪行，可處監禁3年。」</span><br />\n<br />\n但有看報導便知，其實凶徒曾經在行凶前於連儂牆附近踩線，亦代表是早有預謀，而是次有預謀及有意圖的行凶其實是可以《侵害人身罪條例》更嚴重的第17條作檢控<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第17條<br />\n「意圖造成身體嚴重傷害而射擊、企圖射擊、傷人或打人<br />\n任何人意圖使任何人受殘害、外貌毀損、成為傷殘或身體受其他形式的嚴重傷害，或意圖抗拒或防止任何人受到合法拘捕或扣留而 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)以任何方式非法及惡意傷害任何人或導致任何人身體受嚴重傷害；或<br />\n(b)向任何人射擊；或<br />\n(c)拉動扳機或以任何其他方式，企圖用上膛槍械向任何人發射，<br />\n即屬犯可循公訴程序審訊的罪行，可處終身監禁。」</span><br />\n<br />\n第19條及第17條的分別是最大刑罰是監禁三年及終身監禁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以在這裏呼籲TKO的各位同伴，<br />\n如果曾經在連儂牆附近見過凶徒出現，請聯絡警方提供資料及線索，希望能把凶徒改以第17條檢控。<br />\n為當日遇襲的三位同伴討回公道。</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果近月各位對警方的執法及操守有存疑，不想直接聯絡警方，其實亦可以找議員協助。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝"},{"pid":"5061cd9997b3c20bea28da238c3ba9f41cdfab81","tid":1496644,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:23:34.000Z","msg":"一句講晒 9月1 - 2 機場見<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1496431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1496431</a>"},{"pid":"60126e868aab1bf1a50792d7c5f0a19702291caf","tid":1496644,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"意圖謀殺"},{"pid":"d48099efa9f758fca3675afd97f1127341350f87","tid":1496644,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:24:08.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU！而家搭車犯法呀？</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9EGvnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9EGvnL.jpg&h=9da42bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKSEg2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKSEg2M.jpg&h=20a2e6bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/now5W2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnow5W2M.jpg&h=db034c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rC19Ef7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrC19Ef7.jpg&h=5ab15f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUdLW2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUdLW2O.jpg&h=132e85dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBGBjf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBGBjf8.jpg&h=8a441805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />