s=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1496029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1496029</a>"},{"pid":"785b771d5ab1af5491931f362e2d6ee6e554dea2","tid":1496644,"uid":249243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:47:53.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"969662ee902700b42c3e2fd8b7820572ae65b4ce","tid":1496644,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T03:52:03.000Z","msg":"要大肆宣傳set 一個deadline.<br />\n講明<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>若果deadline前政府都唔回應五大訴求, 會行動升級</strong></span> 後果自負<br />\n<br />\n用意: 先小人後君子<br />\n1)迫使政府回應<br />\n2)市民有心理準備當日會有行動<br />\n3)令市民知道當天有行動係源於政府唔回應 <br />\n    (令佢地明白若果政府肯回應就唔會有行動阻礙到佢番工, 出街)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1) 五大訴求</strong><br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況, 解散、追究及重組警隊<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n[下一步棋] 救香港 Set Deadline 行動升級 (幫推)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497453</a>"},{"pid":"2a18a18e824aa1f0f9efbf793a7ccaeb29bd6ec7","tid":1496644,"uid":40309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:36:34.000Z","msg":"推阿，咁都只係坐最多3年，咩世界"},{"pid":"b3d3653b1b5a5f55abc823757a95c87d5aa18593","tid":1496644,"uid":25108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:38:15.000Z","msg":"佢用插既方式攻擊個女仔<br />\n已經係意圖謀殺啦<br />\n帶2把刀,事後換衫走<br />\n已經係畜意啦"},{"pid":"64d9907843a5c9eef7bf86f2926e2857522bb681","tid":1496644,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:38:50.000Z","msg":"推？老妨黎"}]}